As people spend more and more time on such social media sites , the importance of face-to-face human contacts has decresed .
As people feel more confident online where they do not have to face in real-life on the spot , they feel more comfortable and thus prefer communicating online .
This results in the lack of interpersonal skills in the individuals , especially young students as they always have an option to turn their backs to the real-life and go online .
This becomes a huge problem when they have no choice but have to face things in real life .
